ription>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131786469.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Taiwan's defence ministry reported six Chinese navy vessels encircling the island early Wednesday, a day after a similar sighting. Taipei is bolstering its defences, planning to significantly expand its anti-ship missile stockpile by 2029. This comes as Taiwan's first domestically built submarine begins new sea trials, underscoring its commitment to national security amidst ongoing regional tensions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/taiwan-detects-6-chinese-naval-vessels-operating-around-its-territory/articleshow/131786469.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/taiwan-detects-6-chinese-naval-vessels-operating-around-its-territory/articleshow/131786469.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T11:11:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131787587,imgsize-160870.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Texas plane crash: Video captures rescuers trying to free people through cockpit window]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131786177.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-plane-crash-video-captures-rescuers-trying-to-free-people-through-cockpit-window/articleshow/131786177.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/texas-plane-crash-video-captures-rescuers-trying-to-free-people-through-cockpit-window/articleshow/131786177.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T10:04:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131786404,imgsize-593996.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[The world has 193 countries, but only one is named after a real woman; story begins nearly 1,700 years ago]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131786230.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-world-has-193-countries-but-only-one-is-named-after-a-real-woman-story-begins-nearly-1700-years-ago/articleshow/131786230.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-world-has-193-countries-but-only-one-is-named-after-a-real-woman-story-begins-nearly-1700-years-ago/articleshow/131786230.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T10:04:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131786387,imgsize-116252.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[No nukes, Hormuz access and more: JD Vance outlines 3 pillars of US-Iran deal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131785684.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Vice President JD Vance revealed a three-point peace framework with Iran: no nuclear weapons, open Strait of Hormuz, and strict conditions for economic benefits. Tehran must cease supporting militant groups and abandon its nuclear program to receive aid. Washington emphasizes actions over promises, stating the US benefits regardless of Iran's response.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-nukes-hormuz-access-and-more-jd-vance-outlines-3-pillars-of-us-iran-deal/articleshow/131785684.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-nukes-hormuz-access-and-more-jd-vance-outlines-3-pillars-of-us-iran-deal/articleshow/131785684.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T09:27:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131785708,imgsize-107412.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US military strikes another suspected drug-trafficking boat in eastern Pacific, 1 killed]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131785133.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US forces have killed one suspected drug trafficker in a boat strike in the eastern Pacific, part of a broader anti-narcotics campaign. This incident marks at least 208 deaths since the Trump administration's operations began. Critics question the effectiveness and legality, citing land-based trafficking routes and limited evidence of 'narcoterrorist' claims, with a Pentagon review underway.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-military-strikes-another-suspected-drug-trafficking-boat-in-eastern-pacific-1-killed/articleshow/131785133.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-military-strikes-another-suspected-drug-trafficking-boat-in-eastern-pacific-1-killed/articleshow/131785133.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T08:41:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131785445,imgsize-16071711.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From robbery to chase to four bullets: How Pakistan police's 'mistaken assessment' killed a 9-year-old Australian girl]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131784456.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A family visit to Pakistan turned tragic when nine-year-old Australian 