h]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131781373.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-techie-sai-karthik-varma-datla-among-12-people-killed-in-missouri-plane-crash/articleshow/131781373.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-techie-sai-karthik-varma-datla-among-12-people-killed-in-missouri-plane-crash/articleshow/131781373.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T02:05:15+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131781385,imgsize-84072.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What would you do on a Saturday night in Boston? Former US diplomat says F-1 visa can be rejected by this one question]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131781307.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-would-you-do-on-a-saturday-night-in-boston-former-us-diplomat-says-f-1-visa-can-be-rejected-by-this-one-question/articleshow/131781307.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-would-you-do-on-a-saturday-night-in-boston-former-us-diplomat-says-f-1-visa-can-be-rejected-by-this-one-question/articleshow/131781307.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-17T01:45:05+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131781318,imgsize-92780.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[MrBeast’s $1M challenge winner Philip DeFranco plans massive giveaway for subscribers]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;ma